---
By: Ramana Maharshi
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 408
    Verse: 14
Tags:
  - Search/Look Within
---
Look within. Seek the Self. There will be an end of the world and its
miseries. ... The enquiry “Who am I?” is the only method of putting an end
to all misery and ushering in supreme Beatitude.
